The evidence with the title 'A false claim of a medicare change - factcheck.org ' says Mar 27, 2014  ... You must be admitted by your primary physician in order for Medicare to pay for it ! If you are admitted by an emergency room doctor it is treated as outpatient care where hospital costs are not covered . This is only the tip of the iceberg for Obama Care . Just wait to see what happens in this year and 2014! 
